	</script><div class="l-full spacer-top-10"><span class="is-invisible" id="js-searchTotal">5</span><div><div class="l-three u-left sticky-leftnav"><h3 class="section-heading">Most Popular</h3><ul class="left-nav navi spacer-top-20 u-left"><li class="left-nav_item first-item"><a href="/history/2009/april/was-easter-borrowed-from-pagan-holiday.html" class="section"><div class="title title-4_bolded">Was Easter Borrowed from a Pagan Holiday?</div>
