							The Synod of Dort Was Protestantism’s Biggest Debate
							</h1><div class="deck l-nine" itemprop="description">Why Arminians and Reformers squared off 400 years ago.</div>
<div class="featured-article"><img itemprop="image" src="https://www-images.christianitytoday.com/images/114358.jpg?w=700" srcset="https://www-images.christianitytoday.com/images/114358.jpg?w=1400 2x" width="700" alt="The Synod of Dort Was Protestantism’s Biggest Debate" title="The Synod of Dort Was Protestantism’s Biggest Debate" /><div class="image-credit">
